Rating: 3
Absolutely skip the skewers and use a grill wok for the shrimp, and use a CHARCOAL grill, or there will be little flavor to the shrimp. Charcoal adds such a nice smoky flavor to the shrimp and pineapple. The salsa is better with extra jalapenos and MORE cilantro, not less, but go easy on the onion.

